data.description: Enjoy Outstanding Catalina & Rincon Mountain Views from this 3.8 Acre parcel. Rolling topography with slight elevation making a perfect site for your dream home. Water, natural gas, & electric lines are at lot line. Located in the beautiful Tanque Verde Valley boasting Tanque Verde Schools & no HOA. Private & peaceful yet close to all amenities. Forty-Niner Country Club is just a few minutes away for golf, swimming, exercise, & social activities, plus the Rincon Mountain Grill for dining & drinks. Shopping & services such as Safeway, Walgreens, Starbucks, McDonald's, Urgent Care, dental care, hair salons, & several restaurants are only 10-12 minutes away. Come check it out today! Seller has a full set of construction plans available and ready to go...or you may modify to suit your needs.
